Bachelor topic title:
    Web application for Online Business Promotion

Description of the problem:
    Our application allow users to submit bookings for desired services. Some of the
    businesses present in the application use a third party application for reservations.
    The application integrates the third party solution which has similar functionalities.

Advantages:
    - the existing class are not modified towards creating new context of usage.
    - it is easy to defined adapters for any context

Disadvantages:
    - the solution is based upon multiple inheritance which is not possible in Java
      so for implementing we will use interfaces and composition

